    "Amazon's CodeWhisperer [22] revolutionizes the coding process by offering real-time suggestions ranging from snippets to entire functions.",
    "There are many other works in the literature that provide a brief overview of recent advancements in AI code generators including [9], [7], [18], [21] and [22].",
    "While [20] analyzes 52 relevant studies that have used LLMs for software testing, from both the software testing and LLMs perspectives.",
    "In [11], [23] and [4], authors examine the use of LLM-based code generators in software engineering through literature review, programming tasks, or surveys.",
    "The paper [18] conducted a user study with 24 participants to understand the role of Copilot in programming assignments."
